Package: nola.gov
Title: City of New Orleans Open Data (Socrata SODA) Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the City of New Orleans open data portal
    (data.nola.gov). Covers dataset discovery, SoQL queries, 311 requests, police
    calls for service, permits, code enforcement, use of force, misconduct
    complaints, business licenses, and short-term rentals. Includes LLM context
    injection via nola_context().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    dplyr,
    tibble
